metadata.name: Supercar Model 88 - SPECIAL FOUNDER EDITION
metadata.description:
VirtualiaWorlds is building a virtual economy that allow creators, property developers, businesses and devs build virtual worlds experience on hybrid , multiverse and metaverse worlds.  
Buy a land, a virtual property, avatarize yourself, get luxury assets in a photorealistic world. Vote in the governance and climb the societal ladder to build your empire. Market your brand, perform 3D live concerts or sell real products on your virtual store. Possibilities are endless.  
Owning this unique supercar model, out on sale by the founder, will give you a special place in our community, a special place in our wall of fame in VirtualiaWorlds, direct access to our Gentleman Club membership, a whitelist seat for our STO and ICO and much more benefits.  
This model is special as this is the first minted NFT from VirtualiaWorlds. Of course, you can add your NFS avatar and use the supercar later.  
If you sell your NFT to someone else, you will lose above benefits.

Join our community on Discord: https://discord.gg/ebJtR8fhfG
